OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FThe Edinburgh Filmhouse is to reopen
OL,7,Ftwo years after it closed with the
OL,8,Fhelp of #1.5 million funding from the
OL,9,FUK Government.
OL,11,FThe independent cinema opened in 1979
OL,12,Fin a former Presbyterian Church with
OL,13,Fonly one screen but became a cultural
OL,14,Ficon with a programme compared to the
OL,15,FBritish Film Theatre in London.
