OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FIt closed on October 6, 2022 following
OL,7,Fthe collapse of umbrella company
OL,8,FCentre for the Moving Image and a
OL,9,Fgrassroots campaign began to save it,
OL,10,Fbacked by actors including Ewen
OL,11,FBremner and Brian Cox.
OL,13,FA business model was created to
OL,14,Frelaunch the cinema, with a board of
OL,15,Ftrustees including some who worked
OL,16,Fthere for two decades.
OL,18,FA Crowdfunder which aimed to raise
OL,19,F#300,000 has almost met its target at
OL,20,F#254,430.
