OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FThe trustees learned on March 19 their
OL,7,Fapplication for money from the
OL,8,FLevelling Up Fund was being granted by
OL,9,Fthe UK Government and they are now
OL,10,Fpreparing to sign the lease on May 1
OL,11,Fahead of a huge refurbishment.
OL,13,FPlans include a complete refit, the
OL,14,Faddition of a fourth screen for
OL,15,Feducational use, and reducing the
OL,16,Fseating capacity from 450 to 350 to
OL,17,Fmake it more comfortable, as well as
OL,18,Fincreasing accessibility inside the
OL,19,Fcinema.
