OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FJames Rice, who began working in the
OL,7,Fbox office in 2003 before leaving in
OL,8,F2019, said without the funding the
OL,9,Ffuture would have been uncertain.
OL,11,FMr Rice said: "If we hadn't got the
OL,12,Fgrant, I don't know what the outcome
OL,13,Fwould have been.
OL,15,F"The refit matters because it helps us
OL,16,Fto attract new people in. We want to
OL,17,Ftry to introduce people to a broader
OL,18,Frange of cinema.
