OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,F"The core message is to deliver a full
OL,7,Fprogramme, including documentaries and
OL,8,F2001: A Space Odyssey.
OL,10,F"A large proportion of what we do is
OL,11,Fnot screened at other cinemas.
OL,13,F"We have got to this point because of
OL,14,Fthe strength of feeling and support,
OL,15,Ffrom letter writing and public
OL,16,Fmeetings. There's some people who
OL,17,Fworked here who went onto be film-
OL,18,Fmakers."
