OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FMr Rice said cinema faced new
OL,7,Fchallenges from streaming services and
OL,8,Ffiresticks, but that Edinburgh had
OL,9,Fseen an increase of 33% turnout in
OL,10,Fcinemas over the past year compared to
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FThe Filmhouse described its programme
OL,14,Fas "the most ambitious cultural film
OL,15,Fprogramme outside the British Film
OL,16,FTheatre" in London's Southbank and
OL,17,Falso hosted the Edinburgh
OL,18,FInternational Film Festival for many
OL,19,Fyears.
