OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FOptions are being explored regarding
OL,7,Fpricing, including "pay what you can",
OL,8,Fand efforts are being made to ensure
OL,9,Fcost is not a barrier to accessibility.
OL,11,FTrustee Ginnie Atkinson said another
OL,12,F#800,000 has been raised from donors
OL,13,Fand philanthropists but described the
OL,14,FUK Government funding as
OL,15,F"transformational".
OL,17,FShe said plans were afoot to
OL,18,F"modernise" amid complaints the
OL,19,Foriginal seats did not provide enough
OL,20,Fspace and were threadbare.
