OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FMs Atkinson said: "This is absolutely
OL,7,Ftransformational. When we applied the
OL,8,Famount was aspirational. We have to
OL,9,Fattract new audiences and make it a
OL,10,Fmodern, comfortable cinema experience.
OL,12,F"Our aspiration is to open on October
OL,13,F6, the two-year anniversary of it
OL,14,Fclosing. We are hoping before
OL,15,FChristmas."
OL,17,FHowever, she said an opening date
OL,18,Fcould be between six months and a year.
