OL,3,CEdinburgh Filmhouse to reopen with
OL,4,Chelp of #1.5m UK Government funding
OL,6,FScotland Office minister Donald
OL,7,FCameron was given a tour of the
OL,8,Fbuilding and welcomed the funding
OL,9,Fboost.
OL,11,FHe said "communities" which benefited
OL,12,Fincluded artists, international
OL,13,Fstudents and people living outside
OL,14,FEdinburgh.
OL,16,FMr Cameron said: "It's really
OL,17,Fimportant that a facility like this is
OL,18,Faccessible to everyone. People travel
OL,19,Ffrom the Borders to visit. We hope it
OL,20,Fattracts people from across Scotland.
